description:
Is the King James Bible perfect or just &quot;a good translation?&quot;
In this book, Dr. Gipp gives in-depth yet understandable answers on the issue of our inspired Bible. Furthermore, the position is defending by using the Bible, the &quot;final authority in all matters of faith and practice,&quot; not the opinions of men.


Sam Gipp a former Pastor, is an Evangelist, teacher, author and Bible Conference speaker. He has the unique ability to digest large amounts of information and then present it in an analytical, understandable, format. His humorous, informative and forceful preaching style make him popular with all ages and keeps him in demand as a Revivalist and Bible Conference speaker.
